    "title": "Business Post India Capital India is Hiring: Warehouse Manager (Senior)",
    "description": "Business Post India Capital India invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Warehouse Manager at our Srinagar location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Business Post India Capital India:\nBusiness Post India Capital India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Business Post India Capital India!",
